      "comment": "LOOK FOR TASCOTT (4) has recorded two wins and two minor placings from the past five starts. Added to his reputation at his latest appearance when he got the job done by 3.5 metres over 2138m at this track. Finds a suitable assignment and will prove very tough to beat once more. PIZZA PRINCE (5) made it two wins from two runs this prep last start when he got the cash by a head over 2138m here. Leading hope based on recent form. NELLIE JOY (8) has been thereabouts of late and is a great chance to break through. Good effort last time out when she finished second at this circuit over 2138m. One for the exotics players. FENOMENAL (6) is heading the right way, improving last time out to finish third at this course over 2138m. May earn some minor money.",
